ZH: 我今天特别劳累，需要好好休息。
EN: I am especially tired today and need a good rest.

ZH: 他一整天劳累地工作，下班后几乎没有时间休息。
EN: He works hard all day and hardly has any time to rest after work.

ZH: 老师整天工作劳累，但是仍然非常有精神地教学。
EN: The teacher is tired from working all day, but still teaches with great enthusiasm.

ZH: 做家务很劳累，但是可以让家变得整洁。
EN: Doing household chores can be tiring, but it can make the home tidy.

ZH: 考试前的备考阶段非常劳累，但是能让你获得好成绩。
EN: The preparation stage before exams is very tiring, but it can help you achieve good grades.

ZH: 他的工作很劳累，每天都要面对很多挑战。
EN: His job is very demanding, and he faces many challenges every day.

ZH: 劳累的身体需要充足的睡眠来恢复。
EN: A tired body needs sufficient sleep to recover.

ZH: 长时间的照顾孩子对妈妈来说非常劳累。
EN: Taking care of children for long periods of time is very tiring for mothers.

ZH: 游览名胜古迹后，我们感到很劳累，但是非常满足。
EN: After visiting famous scenic spots, we feel tired but very satisfied.

ZH: 公司发放了一周假期来缓解员工的劳累。
EN: The company gave a week off to relieve the employees' fatigue.

ZH: 长时间专注于任何事情都会让人感到劳累。
EN: Focusing on anything for a long time can make a person tired.

ZH: 手工艺品制作需要耗费大量的体力，非常劳累。
EN: Making handicrafts requires a lot of physical strength and is very tiring.

ZH: 没有适当的休息，劳累会对身体造成伤害。
EN: Without proper rest, fatigue can harm the body.

ZH: 运动是劳累和放松的完美结合。
EN: Exercise is the perfect combination of exertion and relaxation.

ZH: 长途旅行经常使人感到劳累，但是也能带来很多乐趣。
EN: Long-distance travel often makes people tired, but it also brings a lot of fun.

ZH: 长时间的工作会使人身心劳累。
EN: Long hours of work can make a person mentally and physically exhausted.

ZH: 劳累让人更加珍惜休息的时间。
EN: Fatigue makes people appreciate their rest time even more.

ZH: 心理压力会加重人的劳累感。
EN: Psychological stress can intensify a person's sense of fatigue.

ZH: 劳累的身体需要适当的营养来恢复体力。
EN: A tired body needs proper nutrition to regain strength.

ZH: 休息不充足会导致长期的劳累感。
EN: Insufficient rest can lead to long-term fatigue.
